{"_path":"/resident/r020","_dir":"resident","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"道路安全隱患","description":null,"image":"/images/resident/r020-01.jpeg","sequence":20,"category":"道路安全","place":"A7重劃區","author":"社區網站","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 "},{"name":"og:title","content":"社區網站-地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-09-02T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"道路安全隱患"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"道路安全隱患"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主旨: 長庚醫療社區大門前長期違停, 造成行人交通安全隱患。請排除！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n說明:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市龜山區長庚里 長庚醫護社區大門前 是文德路及長庚路 三個主要道路交匯點(如圖 1)。 在文德路轉彎處形成死角, 長期有商店招牌及車輛違停。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"違停造成車輛轉彎時無法看到穿越斑馬線的行人, 也容易忽視文德路雙方轉彎車輛。造成交通安全隱患！如圖 2 ~ 4。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由長樂公園 通往文德路的行人道被路障阻擋, 只留小通道 如圖 5。 造成道路轉彎處死角, 讓車輛長期違停！及拉圾囤放區。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"辦法:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建議在此轉彎死角標示紅線, 並請巡邏警察加強取締！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建議將路口行人道路障移除 （圖 5），改為黃色塑膠立桿。方便行人通行, 但阻止機車, 自行車進入！"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r020-01.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r020-01.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":" 圖 1\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r020-02.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r020-02.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","va